About project file:

THis is a JAVAFX project it require JAVAFX framework;
javafx is preinstalled in Intellij IDE's with scene editors too.
just open project in ANY IDE's(or Intellij)with JAVAFX framework and run.


Server folder:

This also include a server folder  which contain server.java file which can be compiles and run in console.
The IP of machine running the server file will act as server for all clients ;





Running the program:

open program and run.should type the address of server in config page.

After config page enter address of user u want to connect @(ip of user to chat)@
The user also should be connected to the server


key words:

@close@:to close connectioj with one user







 

